Ranger Help for: camoflage
==========================

SYNTAX:      camo
             camoflage
USAGE:       Wilderness
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     55
SKILL TYPE:  stealth

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to use advanced natural camouflage to become
nearly invisible in wilderness terrain. Camoflage provides a higher
level of concealment than the basic conceal skill, making the Ranger
much harder to detect. The Ranger must not be in combat to activate
this skill. Moving or attacking will break the camouflage. This skill
is ideal for setting up ambushes or bypassing dangerous areas unseen.
